<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Resolve Admin Reminder</title>
  <style>
    /* General Styles */
    body, html {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #000000;
    }
    
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    /* Container */
    .container {
      max-width: 420px;
      margin: 10px auto;
      border: 1px solid #dddddd;
    }
    
    /* Header */
    .header {
      height: 87px;
      background-color: #002347;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    
    .header-content {
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .logo {
      height: 26.59px;
      width: 109px;
    }
    
    .website {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #cccccc;
    }
    
    /* Banner */
    .banner {
      height: 86px;
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #EEEDF8;
      padding: 0 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .banner-content {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .banner-text h2 {
      max-width: 236px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #000000;
    }
    
    .banner-text p {
      width: 220px;
      font-size: 8px;
      margin: 5px 0 0 0;
      color: #1F2124;
    }
    
    .banner-image {
      margin-bottom: -6px;
      height: 60px;
    }
    
    /* Main Content */
    .main-content {
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    
    .main-title {
      padding: 16px 0;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    .greeting {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    .intro {
      padding: 8px 0;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #1F2124;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    /* Features Section */
    .features-section {
      padding: 0 20px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    
    .features-title {
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .feature-item {
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    
    .check-icon {
      height: 13px;
      width: 13px;
      background-color: #90B5FF;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: white;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    
    .feature-text {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #1F2124;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    .feature-span {
      color: #3a3c40;
      font-weight: normal;
    }
    
    /* Closing */
    .closing p {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #1F2124;
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    
    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      margin-top: 8px;
      height: 161px;
      background-color: #002347;
      padding: 24px 20px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    
    .footer-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    
    .footer-logo-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .footer-logo {
      height: 13.31px;
      width: 56.61px;
    }
    
    .footer-tagline {
      font-size: 8px;
      color: #cccccc;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    
    .social-icons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 4px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .social-icon {
      height: 16.6px;
      width: 16.6px;
      background-color: #808080;
      border-radius: 50%;
      padding: 4px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .footer-divider {
      margin-top: 12px;
      height: 1px;
      width: 100%;
      background-color: rgba(203, 213, 225, 0.1);
    }
    
    .footer-bottom {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 8px 0;
    }
    
    .footer-description {
      margin-top: 8px;
      width: 164px;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #cccccc;
    }
    
    .copyright {
      font-size: 8px;
      color: #cccccc;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="header">
      <div class="header-content">
        <div>
          <img src="https://placehold.it/109x27" alt="resolve-logo" class="logo">
        </div>
        <span class="website">https://resolve.vote/</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main>
      <!-- Banner -->
      <div class="banner">
        <div class="banner-content">
          <div class="banner-text">
            <h2>Resolve it all—easy elections, trusted results</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, contact our support team at info.resolvevote@gmail.com.</p>
          </div>
          <img src="https://placehold.it/60x60" alt="vote" class="banner-image">
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="main-content">
        <h2 class="main-title">Election Update: Don't Forget to Monitor Your Resolve Election</h2>
        <p class="greeting">Hi {{adminEmail}},</p>
        <p class="intro">This is a quick reminder that your online election on Resolve is currently active.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Features Section -->
      <section class="features-section">
        <h3 class="features-title">Here's what you can do:</h3>
        <div>
          <!-- Feature 1 -->
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="check-icon">✓</div>
            <p class="feature-text">
              Monitor Participation: 
              <span class="feature-span">Log in to your admin dashboard to track voter activity.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Feature 2 -->
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="check-icon">✓</div>
            <p class="feature-text">
              Send Final Reminders: 
              <span class="feature-span">Consider sending an automated follow-up email to voters who haven't cast their votes with resolve</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Feature 3 -->
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="check-icon">✓</div>
            <p class="feature-text">
              Review Results: 
              <span class="feature-span">Once voting closes, review the final tallies directly in Resolve.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Closing -->
      <div class="main-content closing">
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is here to help.</p>
        <p>Thanks for choosing Resolve to power your election!</p>
        <p>
          <span style="display: block;">Best regards,</span> 
          The Resolve Team
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="footer-top">
        <div class="footer-logo-container">
          <div>
            <img src="https://placehold.it/57x13" alt="resolve-logo" class="footer-logo">
          </div>
          <span class="footer-tagline">
            Secure Elections, <br> Trusted Results
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="social-icons">
          <div class="social-icon">
            <svg width="8" height="8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <rect width="24" height="24" fill="white"/>
